body:
### [WorldWindExplorer](https://github.com/emxsys/WorldWindExplorer)
The Emxsys - World Wind Explorer is a geo-browser web app framework based on the [NASA Web World Wind SDK](https://github.com/NASAWorldWind/WebWorldWind). It is an HTML5 web app built with Knockout and Bootstrap libraries. This project is a fork of the [NASA - World Wind Explorer](https://github.com/NASAWorldWindResearch/WorldWindExplorer).

### Authors and Contributors
Emxsys projects are authored by Bruce Schubert (@emxsys)
